# Nasher JSON sources

- Files under `src/` are produced by `nasher unpack` or authored as Nasher-compatible JSON.
- Validate JSON before commit: `python3 -m json.tool <file>` or MCP `nwn.nasher.validate`.
- Resrefs must be unique within their resource type; use `nwn.nasher.resource_lookup` to check collisions.
- Module properties live in `src/module/module.ifo.json` — event script fields use script resrefs without `.nss`.
- Dialog, blueprint, and area JSON follow Nasher field names — do not invent ad-hoc schema keys.

## Do not

- Commit generated `.mod`/`.hak` instead of editing JSON source.
- Hand-edit binary GFF outside the Nasher/Aurora round-trip without documenting why.
